resources.string: Empeereza z’okutuuka ku bantu zikozesebwa naye tezikola, osobola okugezaako okuddamu okusobozesa oba okuddamu okutandika essimu yo
Eremereddwa okusobozesa empeereza y\'okutuukako n\'enkizo z\'ekikolo
Kozesa empeereza ey’omu maaso okukuuma app yo ng’ekola
Emirimu gy’empeereza y’okutuuka ku bantu girina okusobozesa okukola (reserved) .
Olina okuggulawo eddirisa eritengejja okulaba ekiwandiiko (ekintu ekiterekeddwa) .
Ekisumuluzo kya Volume up kiyimiriza script zonna
Oluvannyuma lw\'okuggulawo, okuddukanya script kujja kuggulawo otomatika empeereza y\'okutuuka ku nsonga n\'enkizo za Root (ekintu ekiterekeddwa) .
Ssobozesa mu ngeri ey\'otoma empeereza ezirina enkizo z\'ekikolo
Okwekenenya ensengeka kunywevu nnyo nga kusobozeseddwa, naye omuwendo omutono ogw\'ebiwandiiko guyinza obutakola bulungi. Ddamu okutandika empeereza y\'okutuuka ku bantu okutandika okukola
Kozesa script butereevu oluvannyuma lw’okuggulawo app
Enkolagana ya log telagibwa, era obuwagizi bwa script bwetaagisa okuggulawo enkolagana eno omulundi oguddako
Password erina okuba nga esukka ennukuta 5

Sofutiweya yeetaaga okuggulawo \"Accessibility Services\" okukola, nsaba oggulewo \"Settings->Accessibility Services\" oba \"Settings->Accessibility Services->More Downloaded Services\", funa \" %s \", era okole Empeereza z\'Okutuukako
Empeereza z’okutuuka ku bantu zeetaaga okusobozesa
